{"tid":2087813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"展示藍白旗會觸犯港區國安法","createTime":"2020-06-30T23:42:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T00:47:31.000Z","uid":74368,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ac41ba43ff16d334887cfedccf9b1aeeb647cf99","tid":2087813,"uid":74368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T23:42:48.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】七一遊行前夕，「港區國安法」昨晚11時刊憲生效，據悉警方昨深夜向約300名指揮級警官發出執法指引。警方消息人士稱，倘若今日遊行中有人展示香港獨立旗、<span style=\"color: red;\">俗稱藍白旗的「香港國國旗」</span>，以及印有「香港獨立」或「香港人建國」等字眼相關的旗幟或橫額，以至台獨、疆獨、藏獨的旗幟或橫額（見圖），都會觸犯港區國安法，而在場叫相關口號亦可墮入法網。今日警方執法前會展示一支紫色警告旗，若有涉嫌違反港區國安法的行為，警方會嚴正執法，拘捕前未必會先警告。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20200701/s00001/1593543870034/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200701%2Fs00001%2F1593543870034%2F&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwEPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=fecbc5cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200701%2Fs00001%2F1593543870034%2F&h=441bd10e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20200701/s00001/1593543870034/</a>"},{"pid":"912ed0acdabe3ceaadd260fca4d3695356ffca06","tid":2087813,"uid":50386,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T23:44:10.000Z","msg":"佢唔講都冇人知藍白旗係「香港國國旗」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d45a36a632a2ac32c55353c42e842a2a5e3181e","tid":2087813,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T23:44:14.000Z","msg":"英女王喜好紫色喎&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"9fe2498d567900fa469b923f4b324ff531d9cfaf","tid":2087813,"uid":227788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T23:44:52.000Z","msg":"黃黑呢?"},{"pid":"2c468dcefb6887de42fc1730207b777cd70a191f","tid":2087813,"uid":13844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime